Subject: [PATCH] Add Trading Dashboard panel with market data and trade alerts

Features:
- Real-time market overview (S&P 500, NASDAQ, VIX, Forex, Crypto, Gold)
- Watchlist tracking major tech stocks (AAPL, MSFT, GOOGL, TSLA, NVDA)
- Trade alerts with signal detection, execution status, and risk warnings
- Agent consensus scoring (Trend, Momentum, Volatility, Risk, Strategy)
- Market news feed from major financial sources
- Performance metrics (win rate, R multiple, profit factor, drawdown)
- Risk management display (position size, daily limits, account status)
- System status monitoring (agent fleet, decision engine, memory sync)
- Dark theme matching existing Lantern OS aesthetic
- Fully responsive grid-based layout

The trading panel integrates with Lantern OS's existing convergence engine,
CSF memory system, and PCSF safety framework for decision logging and
long-term pattern tracking. Paper trading mode by default.

